title: Jinx christmas skin (IS A MUST)
body:
Jinx as the grinch
1820 legendary skin
(brand is the halloween one)
her mini gun is a christas tree+pot
rocket launcher is a large wraped box
her W is a candy cane
Her E are wrapped boxes and it makes her say "got a present for ya"
her ult is a large christmas tree and some rockets are attacked around it to make it fly.
Her ult makes her say Merry christmas
or "Have a nice year"
Her joke "Christmas isnt ruined, I mean yet"
Taunt "Next year will be a great year with you"
Her W or ult could make her say "Suprise"

Please spread it along

replies.body: Her ult could also say "I got you a present!"
Her Ult cousd say Surprise when she kills the target
Jethus (Jesus Karthus) is what we need.

HAPPY BIRTHDAY!
